1. Open Putty SSH Client

2. Check the ip address of the raspberry pi using "Fling" app in your smartphone.

3. Enter the ip address of the pi in Putty.

4. Login as: pi
   Password: Iamashish1234

5. Create a vncserver from the pi by typing in the command: tightvncserver

6. Open the terminal and type in the command: vncviewer

7. Enter the ip address of the pi and ":1" as shown when we executed the tightvncserver command in the pi.

8. Enter the password: Iamashish1234
